Package: tiltR
Title: Fermentation forecast dashboard using the Tilt Hydrometer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Owen",
           family = "Daniel",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "owendnl@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides an R Shiny app to visualise statistics for an ongoing fermentation using the Tilt Hydrometer. The dashboard includes the ability to view forecast fermentation profiles, derived using a logistic model with Bayesian parameter estimation through Stan. 
